{"tid":2379711,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"SpaceX火箭載逾百衛星升空破紀錄　分析指商機大","createTime":"2021-01-25T11:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:59:36.000Z","uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6eea0e35ce94ce0e9cf0d8880445f3121225c839","tid":2379711,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bd3vmHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBd3vmHY.jpg&h=45398d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太空探索技術公司SpaceX的獵鷹運載火箭，在美國佛羅里達州升空，將一批共143個人造衛星發射到太空，打破單次發射攜帶最多人造衛星升空的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n獵鷹搭載的人造衛星，包括48個地球成像衛星、17個微型通信衛星、30個為美國及歐洲地區服務的小型衛星，以及SpaceX旗下「星鏈」計劃的10個人造衛星。SpaceX的目標是發射1000個「星鏈」衛星，形成網絡，向地面提供高速互聯網服務。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">SpaceX的發射計劃標榜廉價，收取每名客戶運送費用後，將不同形狀的小型人造衛星「打包」送上軌道。分析說，今次是人類太空活動一次革命及結構性改變，因為相關企業只需付出相對較低的成本，就可獲得太空空間使用權，日後商機及發展潛力巨大。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對小型衛星發射既吸引力大增<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46414dce58695baf57c747818b9da0872e657f07","tid":2379711,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:41:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572195-20210125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572195-20210125.htm&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=c6de2109\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572195-20210125.htm&h=76da23ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572195-20210125.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bb6c1ff582c0195afd26d1548d47f0c28f825496","tid":2379711,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"IPO IPO IPO"},{"pid":"14c7f2e964bf420d8d6d4feba0bcc3b7b3c987e0","tid":2379711,"uid